17:54.842 --> 17:55.908
Well, Morty, I'd say

17:55.910 --> 17:58.311
   we've invented
a little honesty today.

17:58.313 --> 18:00.045
  How about you?
           I don't deserve this.

18:00.047 --> 18:01.246
          I was just having fun.

18:01.248 --> 18:02.315
          So was Jeffrey Dahmer.

18:02.317 --> 18:04.317
                Speaking of,
          time to pay the piper.

18:04.319 --> 18:06.319
 [ Tires screech, siren wails ]

18:06.321 --> 18:08.854
                Morty Smith.

18:08.856 --> 18:11.324
    Come out with your hands up,
              you sick [bleep]

18:11.326 --> 18:13.192
               We're also fine
          with just shooting you

18:13.194 --> 18:14.994
                if you wanna
               suicide by cop.

18:14.996 --> 18:16.195
                    What?
                What is this?

18:16.197 --> 18:17.730
        Wow.
Looks like a SWAT Team,

18:17.732 --> 18:18.998
 some drug dealers,

18:19.000 --> 18:22.067
some grassroots MeToo activists,
     the ACLU --

18:22.069 --> 18:23.669
    Jesus, Morty,
      the AARP?

18:23.671 --> 18:26.339
               I don't wanna
               talk about it!
The NAACP, GamerGate...

18:26.341 --> 18:29.474
Morty, is that Supreme Court
Justice Sonia Sotomayor?

18:29.476 --> 18:30.809
                 I'm sorry!
               I -- I'm sorry!

18:30.811 --> 18:32.345
                  I-Is that
        what you want me to say?

18:32.347 --> 18:34.747
          What -- What do I do?
Oof, well, I'm stumped.

18:34.749 --> 18:37.082
Seems like there's no way
  out of this one.

18:37.084 --> 18:38.283
      Unless...

18:38.285 --> 18:39.685
                God damn it.

18:39.687 --> 18:41.754
Yeah, I guess it is, uh --
what did you call it?

18:41.756 --> 18:44.089
       Uh, uh,
  "A shitty idea"?

18:44.091 --> 18:46.225
                   God damn it.
Say the vat is good.

18:46.227 --> 18:48.160
              The vat is good.

18:48.162 --> 18:50.263
    Kiss the vat.

18:52.299 --> 18:53.766
       Do not
  go into that vat.

18:53.768 --> 18:55.768
  It appears to be
    full of acid.

18:55.770 --> 18:57.770
             It is!
 Please, he's just a little boy!

18:57.772 --> 19:00.173
       Let me talk to him.
  Tell him
 we're very upset!

19:00.175 --> 19:01.506
   Morty, please.
     Step back.

19:01.508 --> 19:02.908
      That vat
  is full of acid.

19:02.910 --> 19:05.510
It'll melt you completely,
leaving only your bones.

19:05.512 --> 19:07.246
                    Goddamn it!
    I'm sorry,
 what did you say?

19:07.248 --> 19:08.447
           I'm going in the vat!

19:08.449 --> 19:11.183
     [ Indistinct shouting ]

19:11.185 --> 19:14.387
            Oh! God!
       Aw, I blame myself!

19:14.389 --> 19:16.188
       Oh, what a tragedy.

19:16.190 --> 19:18.457
             This --
    Oh, well, he's bones now.

19:18.459 --> 19:19.658
   I guess all debts are paid.

19:19.660 --> 19:21.394
                   Agreed.
           He's definitely dead.

19:21.396 --> 19:23.796
      Why else
would the bones come up?

19:23.798 --> 19:25.731
              While his actions
               were horrifying

19:25.733 --> 19:28.401
          and we are well within
      our rights to be outraged,

19:28.403 --> 19:30.803
          I do wonder if we bear
             some responsibility

19:30.805 --> 19:33.005
             for this young man
        melting himself in acid.

19:33.007 --> 19:35.874
      Are we here for justice...
             or something else?

19:35.876 --> 19:39.211
"Though justice be thy plea,
   consider this,

19:39.213 --> 19:41.346
 that in the course
    of justice...

19:41.348 --> 19:44.016
     none of us
should see salvation.

19:44.018 --> 19:45.484
We do pray for mercy."

19:45.486 --> 19:46.819
      "Merchant of Venice,"
              nice.

19:46.821 --> 19:48.421
           Very cool.
      Lots to think about.

19:48.423 --> 19:50.223
Vengeance is a tomb,
all-encompassing --

19:50.225 --> 19:53.759
   Alright, okay, this isn't a
poetry reading, a kid just died.

19:53.761 --> 19:57.230
 Every -- Everybody go home and
hug your loved one or something.

19:57.232 --> 20:02.167
    [ Vehicle doors closing,
       engines starting ]

20:02.169 --> 20:03.436
              Wait.

20:03.438 --> 20:04.770
         How do we know
       that's really acid

20:04.772 --> 20:06.705
    and you didn't just have
    someone's bones in there?

20:06.707 --> 20:08.307
      I mean, if you're doubting
           if that's really acid

20:08.309 --> 20:09.975
     and not just jacuzzi-heated
                Mountain Dew,

20:09.977 --> 20:11.576
               you're welcome
             to use this ladle.

20:11.578 --> 20:13.446
            You think
      I'm a goddamn idiot?

20:13.448 --> 20:15.681
         Brought my own.

20:20.387 --> 20:21.654
              Aah!

20:21.656 --> 20:22.855
      Oh, God!
     Oh, God no!

20:22.857 --> 20:24.589
    Oh, God, no!
   Oh, no -- Huh?

20:24.591 --> 20:26.125
               I'm acid-proof!

20:26.127 --> 20:28.260
             [Bleep] all of you
             [bleep] all of you,

20:28.262 --> 20:29.462
             I'm gonna be rich!

20:29.464 --> 20:30.796
               Here's my ass.

20:30.798 --> 20:32.865
              Take a good look,
                  spank it!

20:32.867 --> 20:34.399
                 Acid proof!

20:34.401 --> 20:37.402
 Feels like that guy
had other stuff going on.

20:37.404 --> 20:40.005
     Don't ever
make fun of me again.

20:40.007 --> 20:41.874
        Ever!

20:41.876 --> 20:43.476
Alright, c'mon Morty,
   let's go home.

20:43.478 --> 20:45.077
                 Wait, what?
 This -- This isn't our reality?

20:45.079 --> 20:46.479
   What, you think
 I'd waste our home

20:46.481 --> 20:48.147
    teaching you
  a [bleep] lesson?

20:48.149 --> 20:49.949
[ Sighs ] I am gonna miss
this place, though --

20:49.951 --> 20:52.084
Johnny Carson's still alive
   and on the air,

20:52.086 --> 20:53.286
9/11 never happened,

20:53.288 --> 20:54.687
and Rocky Road ice cream
  has peanut butter

20:54.689 --> 20:56.755
instead of marshmallows.
                 The fu-- What?

20:56.757 --> 20:58.157
              The marshmallows
             are the best part!

20:58.159 --> 21:00.025
